high_descs: Turn around and face the white table to the right.
Pick the apple on the right up from the white table.
Turn around and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and pick up the apple again and shut the door.
Go left and then turn right to face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around to your left then walk straight then face the table
Pick up the apple on the table
Turn around to your left and face the fridge
Open the fridge put in the apple and take it out then close the fridge
Turn left walk straight head to the sink to your right
Put in the apple in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled apple in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the door, then turn right and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the apple off of the table.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the apple inside on the middle shelf then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the apple, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the chilled apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the sink.
